<section>
<title>Detailed Description</title>

<para>This class creates a very simple virtual file system from a directory. This allows read access to all files in that directory referencing them from their path as a unique identifier. As this doesn&apos;t give the benefits of asset obfuscation, it is only used on debug mode, and can&apos;t be configured at the moment. </para>
</section>
